snippet.title: Theatrhythm Final Fantasy All-Star Carnival (trailer)
snippet.description: Theatrhythm Final Fantasy All-Star Carnival is a rhthym arcade game from Square Enix starring Final Fantasy characters and songs. It will be out in Autumn 2016.
